{"tid":107630,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【一月新番】Rewrite 第二季 04","createTime":"2017-02-04T14:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T08:06:59.000Z","uid":1130,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af30dabf2e375f69daa81cb74fa0035c9189092d","tid":107630,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T14:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.org/n1fa1bbm1/Jn_IN3_Jn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.org%2Fn1fa1bbm1%2FJn_IN3_Jn.jpg&h=022cd7ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n■ STORY<br />\n《Rewrite》故事描述對瑚太朗來說，原本只是抱著一絲絲的冒險心態，只要能和這些吵鬧的同伴們一起度過的話這樣就足夠了。但瑚太朗還沒查覺到，他將和沒有人知道的「真實」的探求相連起來。──能夠改寫她們的命運嗎?<br />\n<br />\n■ STAFF <br />\n原作：Key / VisualArt's <br />\n監督、系列構成：天衝 <br />\n系列構成：田中羅密歐、魁<br />\n腳本：あおしまたかし、髙橋龍也 <br />\n角色原案：樋上いたる<br />\n角色設計：野中正幸 <br />\n音樂製作：VisualArt's <br />\n動畫製作：8bit<br />\n<br />\n■ CAST <br />\n天王寺瑚太朗：森田成一 <br />\n神戶小鳥：齋藤千和 <br />\n鳳千早：篠宮沙彌 <br />\n千里朱音：喜多村英梨 <br />\n中津静流：鈴木惠子<br />\n此花露琪亞：朝樹りさ <br />\n篝：花澤香菜<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逢星期六晚 22:30 (香港時間)<br />\n<a href=\"http://mov3.co/tokyomx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmov3.co%2Ftokyomx%2F&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=fdba7dd2\" target=\"_blank\">http://mov3.co/tokyomx/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zhanqi.tv/meizhi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhanqi.tv%2Fmeizhi&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7c29e933\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.zhanqi.tv/meizhi</a><br />\n<br />\n密切留意 <a href=\"http://viu.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fviu.com&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8ecda1c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://viu.com</a> 及 <a href=\"http://ebb.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Febb.io&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ba74fc7a\" target=\"_blank\">http://ebb.io</a> 更新"},{"pid":"133e01bf74040ede84eb8876b0f400ea0be10bfd","